snippet: Nascar suspended four members of the defending Sprint Cup champion Brad Keselowski’s team and three from his teammate Joey Logano’s for seven races each.
abstract: Nascar suspends four members of Brand Keselowski's team and three from his teammate Joey Logano's for seven races each for using unapproved auto parts in Texas race, dropping Keselowski to 4th and Logano to 14th in Sprint Cup Series standings.
lead_paragraph: Nascar suspended four members of the defending Sprint Cup champion Brad Keselowski’s team and three from his teammate Joey Logano’s for seven races each.
